The '''Ministry of Agriculture, Regional Development and Environment of [[Moldova]]''' ({{Lang-ro|Ministerul Agriculturii, Dezvoltării Regionale și Mediului}}) is one of the nine ministries of the [[cabinet of Moldova|Government of Moldova]].
