{{Infobox Ukrainian raion | name = Sverdlovskyi Raion | Ukrainian_name = Свердловський район | image_skyline = | image_shield = | image_flag = | image_map = Sverdlovskyi-Lug-Raion.png | mapsize = 250px | region = [[Luhansk Oblast]] | region_flag = {{flagicon|Luhansk Oblast}} | coordinates = {{coord|47|56|24|N|39|38|33|E|type:adm2nd_region:UA|display=inline,title}} | city_councils = 0 | town_councils = 1 | village_councils = 6 | villages = 26 | settlements = 3 | date_created = 1938 | population = {{decrease}} 12,039 | population_as_of = 2013 | area_km2 = 1132 | elevation_m = | admin_center = [[Sverdlovsk, Ukraine|Sverdlovsk]] | governor = | raion_phone_code = 6434 | postal_index = 94820—94871 | website = }} {{About|a subdivision of [[Luhansk Oblast]] in the [[Eastern Ukraine]]|other similar subdivisions elsewhere|Sverdlovsky District (disambiguation){{!}}Sverdlovsky District}} '''Sverdlovsk Raion''' ({{Lang-uk|Свердловський район}}) is a [[raion]] (district) in [[Luhansk Oblast]] in eastern [[Ukraine]]. The administrative center of the raion is the town of [[Sverdlovsk, Luhansk Oblast|Sverdlovsk]], which is incorporated separately as a [[city of regional significance (Ukraine)|city of oblast significance]] and does not belong to the raion. Population: {{Ua-pop-est2013|12,039}}.
== History == Since 2014, the raion has been controlled by forces of the [[Luhansk People's Republic]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gkslg.info/files/chisl_0915.pdf|title=Численность населения по состоянию на 1 октября 2015 года по Луганской Народной Республике|publisher=[[Luhansk People's Republic]]|language=Russian|accessdate=21 December 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204211939/http://gkslg.info/files/chisl_0915.pdf|archivedate=4 February 2016|df=}}</ref>
